Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:22:02.23,song_CN_ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}今天卻還是許下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:08.75,song_CN_ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}無法實現的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:14.06,song_CN_ed,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}不要鬆開
